                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Because it bears repeating every time it comes up.
<br />

<br />
Charmed pets steal 1/3 of the XP their damage share indicates, no matter the situation.
<br />

<br />
If an NPC has only been damaged by pets (no PCs), an additional 75% of the NPC's XP is eaten by the pets.  (possibly multiple pets don't generate this penality).  A blue ceramic band, or damage-root, or other such tool is a good idea in this situation.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
